title: Doctor Who Complete Season 05, 1967-1968, Partick Troughton [Upd
description:
[Update: includes recovered episodes]

All 40 episodes of the 1967/98 season of Doctor Who, featuring the Second Doctor and his companions: Jamie McCrimmon, Victoria Waterfield, and Zoe Herriot. This season is heavily reconstructed.

Reconstructions use photographs taken on set and recovered segments of footage, along with the audio recordings of the episodes, to recreate missing episodes. Visual and audio quality varies depending on the reconstruction.
